Start program
Initialize mercury switch, accelerometer, and ultrasonic sensor

Loop forever:
    If mercury switch is triggered:
        Log "Tilt detected"
        Trigger tamper alert

    If accelerometer detects motion above threshold:
        Log "Motion detected"
        Trigger tamper alert

    If ultrasonic sensor detects object within 30cm:
        Log "Proximity alert"
        Trigger tamper alert

    Wait briefly before next check
End loop
